title: RailWorks 26 German Locos ALL in RWP packages
description:
These have all been tested in Railworks TS2016 IND release on Win7 64 bit and are all working. 

This is all but 3 of the steam editions. If anyone has any of these three working please upload them. They most likely have to have the PreLoad files to work.

I have included a text file and 1080p pictures for each engine and they are all in RWP packages to be installed through the package manager. 

Missing :

DB 1970s Freight

DB BR 143

DB E18


Enjoy!
